{"tid":1671790,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"冷氣軍師對近日分化風一感","createTime":"2019-10-23T16:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T18:07:42.000Z","uid":99069,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8fbc71d64164dc26f9c22fbc4372c6ab40e93b2a","tid":1671790,"uid":99069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:48:46.000Z","msg":"作為一個冷氣連登軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我每日做嘅野就係開下po屌下手足<br />\n呢樣做得唔好 嗰樣做得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近排見到越嚟越多同路人 同我一齊屌手足<br />\n感覺好開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n街上面越嚟越多戇鳩仔<br />\n我見到都好開心<br />\n又多幾個比我屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有好多大channel陪我一齊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲記得運動初期<br />\n大家記得雨革失敗原因 <br />\n我一開聲屌戇鳩仔<br />\n大家即刻同我講不分化不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後仲諗咗句<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做法不完美 可接受 但要改善</span></span><br />\n咁講比我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能場運動歷時太耐 大家已經開始忘記<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家嘅初衷</span></span><br />\n幾個月前見到大家鬧戇鳩仔都會加句 <br />\n遲啲先秋後算賬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家已經開聲鬧咗先算<br />\n望po popo表示好興奮<br />\n唔洗做啲咩 佢地已經自己分化自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都知有時有啲人做埋啲野真係戇撚柒鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但大家要記住不分化不割蓆吖<br />\n佢戇鳩屌一句 屌唔聽就咪撚理佢 之後先算<br />\n有咩傾唔埋三口六面傾好佢<br />\n大家都係手足<br />\n係發完夢三唔識七都會講聲小心嘅手足吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好自己人割自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n柒婆會係屋企自己偷笑㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化不割蓆</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做法不完美 可接受 但要改善</span></div></span>"},{"pid":"626853d65ccc789e6e88b24e046eb0fbae7eed83","tid":1671790,"uid":99069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:49:22.000Z","msg":"自推1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03e4b9e7060c194d9aa8b0176278c713f4ca5db","tid":1671790,"uid":104138,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:49:22.000Z","msg":"係得連登仔先咁易割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到勇武612出現時驚無晒民意又想割<br />\n見到舉美國旗又話驚激嬲中共咩咩柒柒又想割<br />\n見到剩係提trump個名又嚇到即刻上twitter 割<br />\n見到勇武裝修裝裝多左驚搞到民企中資又想割<br />\n見到加泰集會又驚美國會嬲即船頭驚鬼船尾驚賊又想割<br />\n<br />\n屌，上面根本就係班L樣諗多左，聽班軍師走去割運動神早完左啦<br />\n好心啦"},{"pid":"d5ef325a99820007974e6b053df996d0d09ff86d","tid":1671790,"uid":99069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:49:39.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"2129ebd9b5562d341117b52dfafeba6b539698b4","tid":1671790,"uid":99069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c03e4b9e7060c194d9aa8b0176278c713f4ca5db","tid":1671790,"uid":104138,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:49:22.000Z","msg":"係得連登仔先咁易割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到勇武612出現時驚無晒民意又想割<br />\n見到舉美國旗又話驚激嬲中共咩咩柒柒又想割<br />\n見到剩係提trump個名又嚇到即刻上twitter 割<br />\n見到勇武裝修裝裝多左驚搞到民企中資又想割<br />\n見到加泰集會又驚美國會嬲即船頭驚鬼船尾驚賊又想割<br />\n<br />\n屌，上面根本就係班L樣諗多左，聽班軍師走去割運動神早完左啦<br />\n好心啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割唔係口號嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81af032f407a2d9ac02b96806fec8256a0130735","tid